      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VERONICASFANTASY (1) progressing nicely. Opened the campaign with a second in a handicap at this track then got the prize last time by 0.8 lengths in a D5 at this track over 280m (16.94). Returns to the handicaps here and will break from the 9m mark. Can continue the fine run of form. DIXIES MAJESTIC (6) was strongly fancied last time on the back of some good form but finished third (29.98) at this track. Deserves a win and gets his chance. TITANIUM WILDCAT (4) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a HCP on April 18 over 500m at this track behind Knock Zaya beaten 4 lengths (30.24). Must be included in calculations. ACOMB BILLY (5) has been mixing his form of late. Won two starts back at this track then finished out of the placings at his latest appearance in an A5 at this track over 500m (30.00). Returns to a handicap this time and breaks from the back. Not out of contention.",
